title: Converse Wall to Wall: Brooklyn Street Art by Jersey Joe
description:
Jersey Joe headed for Brooklyn, two blocks from Converse Rubber Tracks, to bring his street art talents to the side of Grand and Union. Rooted in the middle of Williamsburg, the piece features a mix of Chucks, fall colors, and characters.

For more on Converse Wall to Wall:
http://www.converse.com/walltowall
